4. Create app/Http/Controllers/BulkController.php:
   - handle(Request $request):
       * validate: action in:publish,draft,delete,label_add,label_remove
         post_ids array|required, label_name string (required if action is label_add/remove)
       * authorize: all post_ids belong to auth user
